column3: CANNOT wait to see this one! Huge congrats to Bettiol and the entire team for conquering Flanders in such epic fashion!!!
Ugggghhh, can't wait for this one.
Can’t wait, also looking forward to the party @Boulder clubhouse
what a cycling.. i became one of a fan of ef education first. was brilliant last night.
Forever bonded in this moment! What a feeling.
Grande Alberto!!! Suban el vídeo, quiero verlo tasas, abrazo desde Bahía Blanca Buenos Aires Argentina!!!
